# Audio to Summary

## Introduction
This application converts audio files into text summaries. It uses advanced speech recognition and natural language processing techniques to provide concise summaries of audio content.

## Installation
1. Clone the repository:
    ```sh
    git clone https://github.com/yourusername/audio-to-summary.git
    ```
2. Navigate to the project directory:
    ```sh
    cd audio-to-summary
    ```
3. Install the required dependencies:
    ```sh
    npm install
    ```

## Usage
1. Place your audio files in the `input` directory.
2. Run the application:
    ```sh
    npm start
    ```
3. The summaries will be generated and saved in the `output` directory.

## Configuration
You can configure the application by editing the `config.json` file. The following options are available:
- `language`: The language of the audio files (default: `en`).
- `summaryLength`: The desired length of the summary (default: `short`).

